<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<h4>Why did you choose Computer Science?</h4>
<p>
    I chose Computer Science because I have always been curious about how
    technology works internally. As software continues to evolve, I find
    motivation in learning how systems are designed, built, and improved.
</p>

<h4>What is the purpose of this application?</h4>
<p>
    This application serves as a front-end focused demonstration of the
    ASP.NET Core MVC framework. It highlights views, controllers, models,
    and Razor syntax without implementing full backend functionality.
</p>

<h4>Does this application use a database?</h4>
<p>
    No. All data displayed in this application is static and passed directly
    from the controller to the view for presentation purposes only.
</p>

<h4>What technologies are used?</h4>
<p>
    The application uses C#, ASP.NET Core MVC, Razor views, HTML, and CSS.
</p>
